hopobject.body: How much is a First Class stamp? coburg north village pharmacy An open meeting was held in the church, attended by over 20 villagers, where it was decided that the church should be kept open; their surge of interest has enabled this. But the decision to stop paying the diocesan quota was the biggest element in being able to keep the church open. Instead, villagers opted to pay what they thought was fair and sustainable.
